e Er.","year":-1738},{"id":"rec3OLh8lIs0yxLC4","ref":"Gen.38.4","text":"And she conceived again, and bare a son; and she called his name Onan.","year":-1737},{"id":"recHkzIksoVpNgtz3","ref":"Gen.38.5","text":"And she yet again conceived, and bare a son; and called his name Shelah: and he was at Chezib, when she bare him.","year":-1736},{"id":"rectmPC50yScrE1TV","ref":"Gen.38.6","text":"And Judah took a wife for Er his firstborn, whose name was Tamar.","year":-1736},{"id":"recfEeYCjbkHGn6WX","ref":"Gen.38.7","text":"And Er, Judah’s firstborn, was wicked in the sight of the LORD; and the LORD slew him.","year":-1736},{"id":"rec34xWImabYc886Y","ref":"Gen.38.8","text":"And Judah said unto Onan, Go in unto thy brother’s wife, and marry her, and raise up seed to thy brother.","year":-1722}]}
